## Keystone Automotive Configuration (Required for Compliance)

# Account number provided by Keystone
KEYSTONE_ACCOUNT_NUMBER=your_account_number_here

# Development environment security key (36-character hex string)
KEYSTONE_DEVELOPMENT_KEY=your_development_key_here

# Production environment security key (36-character hex string)  
KEYSTONE_PRODUCTION_KEY=your_production_key_here

## Optional Configuration

# Custom domain for production
VERCEL_URL=ctc.modworx.online

# Additional security settings
KEYSTONE_API_TIMEOUT=30000
KEYSTONE_RETRY_ATTEMPTS=3

## Environment-Specific Notes

# Development Environment:
# - Uses KEYSTONE_DEVELOPMENT_KEY
# - Register development IP with Keystone
# - Safe for testing and development

# Production Environment:
# - Uses KEYSTONE_PRODUCTION_KEY  
# - Register production IP with Keystone
# - Live customer data and transactions

## Security Best Practices

# 1. Never commit actual keys to version control
# 2. Use different keys for development and production
# 3. Rotate keys periodically
# 4. Monitor key usage and access logs
# 5. Restrict access to production environment variables

